{"id":979,"date":"2026-01-24T20:53:59","date_gmt":"2026-01-24T20:53:59","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/?p=979"},"modified":"2026-03-14T05:04:47","modified_gmt":"2026-03-14T05:04:47","slug":"vote-boldly","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/vote-boldly\/","title":{"rendered":"Vote Boldly"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<section class=\"wp-block-app-block-section-post-banner section-post-banner\"><div class=\"t-cr\"><div class=\"t-box t-box-a\"><h1 class=\"hg\">vote boldly<\/h1><div class=\"i-line\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-box t-box-b\"><div class=\"container-studies\"><div class=\"label-studies\">FORM STUDY<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">branding<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">social media animation<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">kinetic type<\/div><\/div><div class=\"container-roles\"><div class=\"label-roles\">ROLE<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">concept<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">design<\/div><div class=\"t-tag\">motion<\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-box t-box-c\"><div class=\"media-wrapper\"><div class=\"media-overlay\"><div class=\"media-overlay-placeholder--mask\"><div class=\"media-overlay-placeholder--text\">Visit Full Video<\/div><\/div><\/div><a class=\"t-media-wrapper\" href=\"https:\/\/vimeo.com\/1010627739\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><video class=\"t-media\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/featuredworks_voteboldly.mp4\" loop muted playsinline autoplay><\/video><\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"section-post-detail\" class=\"wp-block-app-block-section-post-detail\"><div class=\"t-cr\"><header class=\"t-box-a post-detail__meta\"><div class=\"post-detail__heading\">(PROJECT DETAIL)<\/div><div class=\"post-info\"><div class=\"post-info__item\"><div class=\"post-info__item-background\"><\/div><div class=\"post-info__item-label\">MEDIUM<\/div><div class=\"post-info__item-value\">2D<\/div><\/div><div class=\"post-info__item\"><div class=\"post-info__item-background\"><\/div><div class=\"post-info__item-label\">TOOLS<\/div><div class=\"post-info__item-value\">ADOBE AFTER EFFECTS, PHOTOSHOP<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/header><div class=\"t-box-b post-detail__body\"><nav class=\"post-detail__tabs\"><div class=\"post-detail__tab-dot is--active\"><\/div><ul class=\"post-detail__tab-list\"><div class=\"post-detail__tab is--active\">OVERVIEW<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">CHALLENGE<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">REFLECTION<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">PROCESS<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">AWARD<\/div><\/ul><\/nav><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body\"><ul class=\"post-detail__tab-body-list\"><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item is--active\">Civic Nation&#8217;s &#8220;ALL IN Campus Democracy Challenge&#8221; helps first-time voters by making the process clearer and more accessible.<br><br>Many young voters undecided: not from apathy, but from limited outreach and a lack of trusted information.<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">Create an exciting\/attention-grabbing animation through social media post that would appeal to young first time voters: to push them to get out and vote<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">Always thinking back to the company (their colors for example) and enhancing upon this through bolder and more dynamic animation made the project interesting<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">The design shifted to simplified collage after early drafts did not meet client expectations. Layered imagery and striking text now speak to young voters, highlighting the lasting impact of their voice <\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">ADDY Student Silver Award 2025<\/div><\/ul><\/div><div class=\"post-detail__media-container\"><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/allin_icon_white_fill.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/allin_icon_white_fill.webp\"\/><\/picture><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Screenshot-2026-01-25-at-7.45.28-pm.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Screenshot-2026-01-25-at-7.45.28-pm.webp\"\/><\/picture><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/styleframe2_v03.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/styleframe2_v03.webp\"\/><\/picture><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/aitv_styleframe1.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/aitv_styleframe1.webp\"\/><\/picture><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/aitv_styleframe2.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/aitv_styleframe2.webp\"\/><\/picture><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"wp-block-app-block-section-post-gallery section-post-gallery\"><div class=\"t-cr\"><div class=\"t-box t-box-a\"><h2 class=\"hg\">DESIGN + motion<\/h2><div class=\"i-line\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-box t-box-b\"><div class=\"caption-1\">(INFO)<\/div><div class=\"t-body\">WITH A STRONG CONCEPT BUT unclear DESIGN, I pivoted to COLLAGE. each round pushes the boldness further, to show how vital voting is.<\/div><div class=\"caption-2\">SCROLL DOWN<\/div><\/div><div class=\"t-box t-box-c\"><div class=\"container-media\"><div class=\